com.camerontec.catalys.util.fast.template

Class LargeIdsTemplateRegistry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.util.fast.template.LargeIdsTemplateRegistry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITemplateRegistry

    public class LargeIdsTemplateRegistry
extends Object
implements ITemplateRegistry
    ITemplateRegistry which assumes that templates are registered with discountinuos and possibly large IDs: example (120, 16002, 16003) Compare this to the StandardTemplateRegistry implementation where n templates are stored sequencially in an array with id's 0..n-1.
    Author:
    mmattini
